#### 放置（Droppable）
在任意的 DOM 元素上启用 droppable 功能，并为可拖拽小部件创建目标


    <html>
        <head>
            <title>JQuery UI</title>
            <style>
    			.block {
    			    width: 100px;
    			    height: 100px;
    			    background-color: yellow;
    			    border: 1px solid yellow;
    			}
    			.drop {
    			    width: 100px;
    			    height: 100px;
    			    border: 1px dashed black;
    			    opacity: 0.5;
    			}
    			.droppable-active {
        			     border: 1px solid red;
    			}
    			.droppable-hover {
       		             background-color: red;
    			}
    		</style>
        </head>
